-- v0.5 development series --

- Compatible with Thunderbird 3.next
- Collapse all folders by default for easier, faster sorting.
- Remove the "sample folder pane" images that were confusing and allow changes
to be seen in real-time.
- Updated to work with newer nightlies including addon manager
- Updated locales
- New locales: ja, es-ES, zh-CN, sr, nl, pt...
- Added an extra tab for further customization. *You can now choose the default
startup folder*.
- Switch to GitHub
